e premium between perpetual and spot prices, with payments occurring at the top of each hour. The DEX's order book model ensures transparent price discovery without AMM slippage affecting funding calculations. Sui's sub-second finality enables precise entry and exit timing around funding settlements, crucial for capturing small rate differentials."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
